trans-unit.source: Contains the fields from a parsed resource expression.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder felt fra en analysere uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: When a page is parsed, the values contained in a resource expression are parsed and stored in an instance of the ResourceExpressionFields class.
trans-unit.target: Når en side, analyseres, er verdiene i et uttrykk som ressursen analysere og lagres i en forekomst av klassen ResourceExpressionFields.

trans-unit.source: This ResourceExpressionFields object contains two fields, <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ClassKey%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ResourceKey%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Dette ResourceExpressionFields objektet inneholder to felt, <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ClassKey%2A>og <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ResourceKey%2A>.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ResourceKey%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ClassKey%2A>

trans-unit.source: These fields are drawn from the values of a resource expression in either the explicit (`<%$ Resources: ClassKey, ResourceKey %>`) or implicit (`meta:resourcekey="ResourceKey"`) form.
trans-unit.target: Disse feltene er trukket fra verdiene i et uttrykk i den eksplisitt (`<%$ Resources: ClassKey, ResourceKey %>`) eller implisitte (`meta:resourcekey="ResourceKey"`) skjema.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ClassKey%2A> property identifies the class name of a resource that is mapped to a resource file.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ClassKey%2A>egenskapen identifiserer klassenavnet for en ressurs som er tilordnet til en ressursfil.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ClassKey%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, to reference a resource file named Financial.resx, or a localized version such as Financial.en-GB.resx, the resource expression would appear as `<%$ Resources: Financial, ResourceKey %>`.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en referanse til en navngitt Financial.resx eller en lokalisert versjon for eksempel Financial.en GB.resx ressursfil, ressurs-uttrykket vises som `<%$ Resources: Financial, ResourceKey %>`.

trans-unit.source: After parsing, the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ClassKey%2A> property would return "Financial" as its value.
trans-unit.target: Etter analyse, den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ClassKey%2A>egenskapen returnerer "Økonomisk" som verdi.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ClassKey%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ResourceKey%2A> property identifies the particular key/value pair to be retrieved from the file.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ResourceKey%2A>egenskapen identifiserer bestemt nøkkel/verdi-paret som skal hentes fra filen.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ResourceKey%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the Financial.resx file contains a key called `Currency`, that value could be specified with the resource expression `<%$ Resources: Financial, Currency %>`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis filen Financial.resx inneholder en nøkkel kalt `Currency`, at det kan angi verdi med ressurs-uttrykket `<%$ Resources: Financial, Currency %>`.

trans-unit.source: After parsing, the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ResourceKey%2A> property would return "Currency" as its value.
trans-unit.target: Etter analyse, den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ResourceKey%2A>egenskapen returnerer "Valuta" som verdi.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionFields.ResourceKey%2A>

trans-unit.source: The resource expression is parsed through the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.ParseExpression%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Ressurs-uttrykket analyseres via den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.ParseExpression%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ResourceExpressionBuilder.ParseExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Sensitive information should not be stored in a resource file.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Sensitiv informasjon kan ikke lagres i en ressursfil.

trans-unit.source: Gets the class key for a parsed resource expression.
trans-unit.target: Henter klassen nøkkel for en analysere uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: This method returns the class key for a parsed resource expression.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden returnerer klassen nøkkel for en analysere uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: The class key represents the name of the resource file, and is the value specified before the comma (,) in an expression of the form `<%$ Resources: [Namespace.]ClassKey, ResourceKey $>`.
trans-unit.target: Klassenøkkelen for representerer navnet på ressursfilen og verdi som er angitt før komma (,) i et uttrykk med formatet `<%$ Resources: [Namespace.]ClassKey, ResourceKey $>`.

trans-unit.source: A namespace value for the resource class is optional.
trans-unit.target: Et navneområde for ressursklassen er valgfritt.

trans-unit.source: When a namespace is provided, the namespace and the class key are returned in the ClassKey property.
trans-unit.target: Når et navneområde er angitt, returneres navneområdet og klassenøkkelen i egenskapen ClassKey.

trans-unit.source: The class key cannot contain spaces or double-byte character sets (DBCS).
trans-unit.target: Klassenøkkelen for kan ikke inneholde mellomrom eller dobbel byte tegnsett (DBCS).

trans-unit.source: To reference a resource file named Financial.resx or a localized version such as Financial.en-GB.resx, you would include the resource expression <`%$ Resources: Financial, ResourceKey %>`.
trans-unit.target: En referanse til en ressursfilen Financial.resx eller en lokalisert versjon for eksempel Financial.en GB.resx, vil du ta med ressurs-uttrykket `%$ Resources: Financial, ResourceKey %>`.

trans-unit.source: After parsing, the ClassKey property would return "Financial" as its value.
trans-unit.target: Etter analyse, returnere egenskapen ClassKey "Økonomisk" som verdi.

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Sensitive information should not be stored in a resource file.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Sensitiv informasjon kan ikke lagres i en ressursfil.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the class key, or <xref:System.String> if the class key has not been set.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder klassenøkkelen, eller <xref:System.String>Hvis klassenøkkelen ikke er angitt.</xref:System.String> </xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the resource key for a parsed resource expression.
trans-unit.target: Henter ressurs-nøkkel for en analysere uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: This method returns the resource key for a parsed resource expression.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden returnerer ressurs-nøkkel for en analysere uttrykk.

trans-unit.source: The resource key is the value specified after the comma (,) in an expression of the form `<%$ Resources: ClassKey, ResourceKey %>`.
trans-unit.target: Ressursnøkkelen er verdien som er angitt etter komma (,) i et uttrykk med formatet `<%$ Resources: ClassKey, ResourceKey %>`.

trans-unit.source: The ResourceKey property identifies a particular key/value pair within the resource file mapped to the class key.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ResourceKey identifiserer en bestemt nøkkel/verdi-paret i ressursfilen tilordnet til klassenøkkelen for.

trans-unit.source: For example, if a file named Financial.resx contains a key called `Currency`, that value could be specified with the resource expression `<%$ Resources: Financial, Currency %>`.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis en fil med navnet Financial.resx inneholder en nøkkel kalt `Currency`, at det kan angi verdi med ressurs-uttrykket `<%$ Resources: Financial, Currency %>`.

trans-unit.source: After parsing, the ResourceKey property would return "Currency" as its value.
trans-unit.target: Etter analyse, returnere egenskapen ResourceKey "Valuta" som verdi.

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Sensitive information should not be stored in a resource file.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Sensitiv informasjon kan ikke lagres i en ressursfil.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the resource key, or <xref:System.String> if the resource key has not been set.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder Ressursnøkkelen, eller <xref:System.String>Hvis Ressursnøkkelen for ikke er angitt.</xref:System.String> </xref:System.String>
